All inflections are agglutinative suffices.
Nouns (consonant ending):

NOM	nāgm
ACC	vê
POS	ragn
DAT	memô
PREP	nēva
TEMP	mova
LOC	mûva
VOC	jê

NLR	rū
PL	vu
SG	nij
COL	Ø or mî
SGV	môje or Ø

Verbs only:

AOR	na
PROG	mū
IMM	won

PST	mē
FUT	jaw
PRS	Ø

OPT	mânnār
SJV	nêgn
INT	mêmē

4	Ø
1	nêr
2	nīn
3.AN	wâ
3.INAN	rim

Other agglutinative suffixes:

monvīnu		"can" (implies personal ability)
navêgmme	superlative adj.